Deejay Pierra has announced her comeback tour after taking time off to give birth. The DJ made the announcement on her social page on Instagram where she expressed her delight for the upcoming tour. She however did not state the exact dates and locations. Yo, guys, am super excited about my comeback tour that s starting mid-September .I will be posting the dates and locations and apologies for those who came to Sting Lounge yesterday and didn t find me there. No I was not unwell, unfortunately that is done and I will see you soon during the tour. Love you guys. She wrote.Pierra Makena is currently a co-host on the show Lets Talk Kenya on Ebru TV. email print email print